description: Find out the current security wait times at US airports. Ask Alexa for your airport by its city or 3-letter code, and the skill will check the TSA's public API for last-reported wait times at each airport checkpoint.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask airport security for the wait at SFO
Alexa, ask airport security how long the wait is at EWR
Alexa, ask airport security to check Nashville
name: Airport Security Wait Times
shortDescription: Check security wait times at major US airports.
